{"title":"放置核弹","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5833","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>有n个核弹要放在n个坑内,但是如果连续m个坑都放置核弹,核弹就会爆炸。</p><p>所以,在某些坑内,就不能放置核弹</p><p><br></p><p>输入n和m,求出安全放置核弹的方案(结果可能很大,mod（10^9+7）)。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>两个正整数,n和m。</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>方案数 mod 10^9+7</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4 3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>13<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>可以用记忆化搜索</p><p><br></p><p>2&lt;=m&lt;=n&lt;=1000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}